Green Light Worldwide are looking for ** Full Stack Developer ** to design and
implement operations environments within our delivery team. Working as an
integral part of our team, you will be responsible for utilising your strong
development skills to provide proactive service and solutions to our
customers. ?  
  
The ** Full Stack Developer ** will be collaboratively working within an
innovative multi-disciplined environment, utilising their excellent
communications skills for interacting with vendor and development teams to
