  * Experience with Angular, React, CSS, HTML or T-SQL highly desirable. 
  * Proven commercial experience with development of enterprise web applications. 
  * Experience developing with enterprise search, analysis and reporting applications. 
  * Experience with continuous integration build engines, such as Jenkins, Bamboo, TeamCity, Octopus, CruiseControl and Travis. 
  * Experience with Agile software development/ delivery methodologies. 
  * Experience running mission-critical environments. 
